<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Gestion du Temps – Formation Andeine</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --marine:   #1d1b3a;
      --violet:   #7b227a;
      --beige:    #f3c676;
      --bg:       #faf9f6;
      --text:     #1d1b3a;
      --light:    #f0eee8;
      --white:    #ffffff;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ── HEADER ── */
    header {
      background: var(--marine);
      color: var(--white);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 2rem 3.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    /* Decorative circles echoing the logo */
    header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 420px; height: 420px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(123,34,122,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: -100px; right: -80px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    header::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 240px; height: 240px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(243,198,118,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
      bottom: -60px; left: 30%;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .header-logo img {
      width: 160px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .badge-top {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--violet);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.3em 0.85em;
      border-radius: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.12;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    header h1 em {
      color: var(--beige);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .header-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .meta-chip {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.4em 0.9em;
      border-radius: 2em;
    }

    .meta-chip svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* ── HERO BANNER ── */
    .hero-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--violet) 0%, #4a1649 50%, var(--marine) 100%);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-banner p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .hero-banner strong { color: var(--beige); font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── SECTIONS COMMUNES ── */
    section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .section-label {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--violet);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .section-label::before {
      content: '';
      width: 28px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--beige);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* ── INFOS PRATIQUES ── */
    #infos { background: var(--white); }

    .infos-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .info-card {
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--beige);
    }

    .info-card .ic-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--violet);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .info-card .ic-value {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--marine);
    }

    .info-card .ic-sub {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    /* ── PROGRAMME ACCORDÉON ── */
    #programme { background: var(--bg); }

    .accordion { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

    .acc-item {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(29,27,58,0.06);
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .acc-item:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(29,27,58,0.1); }

    .acc-trigger {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: left;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--marine);
      transition: background 0.18s;
    }

    .acc-trigger:hover { background: rgba(123,34,122,0.04); }

    .acc-num {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--marine);
      color: var(--beige);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .acc-trigger[aria-expanded="true"] .acc-num {
      background: var(--violet);
    }

    .acc-arrow {
      margin-left: auto;
      width: 20px; height: 20px;
      color: var(--violet);
      transition: transform 0.25s;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .acc-trigger[aria-expanded="true"] .acc-arrow {
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    .acc-panel {
      display: none;
      padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    .acc-panel.open { display: block; }

    .acc-panel ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .acc-panel ul li {
      padding: 0.35rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #444;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light);
    }

    .acc-panel ul li::before {
      content: '›';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--beige);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    /* ── MODALITÉS ── */
    #modalites { background: var(--marine); color: var(--white); }
    #modalites h2 { color: var(--white); }
    #modalites .section-label { color: var(--beige); }

    .mod-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .mod-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .mod-card:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.11);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .mod-icon {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .mod-card h3 {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--beige);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .mod-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ── ÉVALUATION ── */
    #evaluation { background: var(--white); }

    .eval-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .eval-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.85rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .eval-dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--violet);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 0.45rem;
    }

    .eval-item p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; }

    /* ── LOCALISATION ── */
    #localisation { background: var(--bg); }

    .map-wrapper {
      background: var(--light);
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 340px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(29,27,58,0.1);
    }

    .map-wrapper iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ── TÉLÉCHARGEMENTS ── */
    #telechargements { background: var(--white); }

    .dl-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .btn-dl {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      padding: 0.85em 1.6em;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    }

    .btn-dl:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }

    .btn-primary { background: var(--marine); color: var(--white); }
    .btn-secondary { background: var(--violet); color: var(--white); }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: #111029;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .footer-brand img {
      width: 130px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-brand p {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .footer-contact h4 {
      color: var(--beige);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .footer-contact p { font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .footer-contact a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); text-decoration: none; }
    .footer-contact a:hover { color: var(--beige); }

    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 2rem auto 0;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    .footer-bottom a { color: var(--beige); text-decoration: none; }
    .footer-bottom a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .header-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .header-logo { order: -1; }
      .header-logo img { width: 120px; }
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .acc-panel { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .fade-up {
      animation: fadeUp 0.55s ease both;
    }

    .fade-up:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .fade-up:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .fade-up:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══════════════ HEADER ══════════════ -->
<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-content">
      <span class="badge-top">Formation professionnelle</span>
      <h1>Gestion<br>du <em>Temps</em></h1>
      <div class="header-meta">
        <span class="meta-chip">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          7 heures · 1 journée
        </span>
        <span class="meta-chip">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
          Intra · Inter · Présentiel · Distanciel
        </span>
        <span class="meta-chip">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          Aucun prérequis
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-logo">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Andeine – Formation Conseil Accompagnement" width="160">
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══════════════ HERO BANNER ══════════════ -->
<div class="hero-banner">
  <p>Reprendre le contrôle de votre agenda, <strong>gagner en efficacité</strong> et mieux piloter votre équipe — en seulement une journée.</p>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════ INFOS PRATIQUES ══════════════ -->
<section id="infos">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Informations pratiques</div>
    <h2>À qui s'adresse cette formation ?</h2>
    <div class="infos-grid">
      <div class="info-card fade-up">
        <div class="ic-label">Public cible</div>
        <div class="ic-value">Chefs d'entreprise</div>
        <div class="ic-sub">Cadres & Managers</div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card fade-up">
        <div class="ic-label">Public cible</div>
        <div class="ic-value">Tout professionnel</div>
        <div class="ic-sub">Aucun prérequis nécessaire</div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card fade-up">
        <div class="ic-label">Durée</div>
        <div class="ic-value">1 jour · 7 heures</div>
        <div class="ic-sub">En présentiel ou à distance</div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card fade-up">
        <div class="ic-label">Prérequis</div>
        <div class="ic-value">Aucun</div>
        <div class="ic-sub">Formation accessible à tous</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label" style="margin-top:2rem;">Objectif pédagogique</div>
    <div style="background:var(--light);border-radius:12px;padding:1.75rem 2rem;border-left:4px solid var(--violet);max-width:780px;">
      <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.65rem;">
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:0.97rem;color:var(--marine);"><span style="color:var(--violet);font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">⚙️</span> Acquérir les outils et méthodes de gestion du temps et celui de ses équipes</li>
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:0.97rem;color:var(--marine);"><span style="color:var(--violet);font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">🔍</span> Identifier et distinguer l'urgent de l'important</li>
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:0.97rem;color:var(--marine);"><span style="color:var(--violet);font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">📊</span> Maîtriser la planification, la hiérarchisation et l'organisation</li>
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:0.97rem;color:var(--marine);"><span style="color:var(--violet);font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">✋</span> Savoir déléguer efficacement et dire non aux sollicitations non prioritaires</li>
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:0.97rem;color:var(--marine);"><span style="color:var(--violet);font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">⚡</span> Reprendre le contrôle de son temps et éliminer les voleurs de temps</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════ PROGRAMME ══════════════ -->
<section id="programme">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Programme détaillé</div>
    <h2>Contenu de la formation</h2>

    <div class="accordion">

      <div class="acc-item">
        <button class="acc-trigger" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggle(this)">
          <span class="acc-num">01</span>
          Maîtriser le temps
          <svg class="acc-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="acc-panel">
          <ul>
            <li>Les différentes lois et principes du temps</li>
            <li>Les 5 clés du succès pour préparer sa journée</li>
            <li>La gestion des priorités : l'urgent et l'important</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="acc-item">
        <button class="acc-trigger" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggle(this)">
          <span class="acc-num">02</span>
          Gérer son temps
          <svg class="acc-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="acc-panel">
          <ul>
            <li>Prévoir, hiérarchiser, planifier</li>
            <li>Les voleurs de temps</li>
            <li>Organiser, déléguer, contrôler &amp; Savoir dire non</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="acc-item">
        <button class="acc-trigger" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggle(this)">
          <span class="acc-num">03</span>
          Gérer ses priorités
          <svg class="acc-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="acc-panel">
          <ul>
            <li>Les techniques de priorisation</li>
            <li>Les outils d'organisation</li>
            <li>L'organisation personnelle</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="acc-item">
        <button class="acc-trigger" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggle(this)">
          <span class="acc-num">04</span>
          Les Outils
          <svg class="acc-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="acc-panel">
          <ul>
            <li>Matrice Eisenhower &amp; méthode Pomodoro</li>
            <li>Agenda, planning hebdomadaire &amp; listes de tâches</li>
            <li>Outils numériques &amp; organisation de l'espace de travail</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════ MODALITÉS ══════════════ -->
<section id="modalites">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Modalités pédagogiques</div>
    <h2>Comment se déroule la formation ?</h2>
    <div class="mod-grid">
      <div class="mod-card">
        <div class="mod-icon">🎭</div>
        <h3>Méthodes actives</h3>
        <p>Jeux de rôles, mises en situation et études de cas pratiques ancrés dans votre réalité professionnelle.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mod-card">
        <div class="mod-icon">💬</div>
        <h3>Quiz interactifs</h3>
        <p>Évaluations dynamiques tout au long de la journée pour ancrer les apprentissages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mod-card">
        <div class="mod-icon">🖥️</div>
        <h3>Présentiel ou distanciel</h3>
        <p>En salle équipée ou à distance via Teams / Zoom / Google Meet. Caméra obligatoire en visio.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mod-card">
        <div class="mod-icon">📁</div>
        <h3>Supports fournis</h3>
        <p>Tous les supports pédagogiques sont mis à disposition en ligne à l'issue de la formation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════ ÉVALUATION ══════════════ -->
<section id="evaluation">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Suivi & évaluation</div>
    <h2>Comment vos progrès sont-ils mesurés ?</h2>
    <div class="eval-list">
      <div class="eval-item">
        <div class="eval-dot"></div>
        <p>Feuilles de présence signées</p>
      </div>
      <div class="eval-item">
        <div class="eval-dot"></div>
        <p>Évaluation diagnostique d'entrée en formation</p>
      </div>
      <div class="eval-item">
        <div class="eval-dot"></div>
        <p>Quiz, travaux individuels et en groupe en cours de session</p>
      </div>
      <div class="eval-item">
        <div class="eval-dot"></div>
        <p>Mises en situation et jeux de rôles</p>
      </div>
      <div class="eval-item">
        <div class="eval-dot"></div>
        <p>Évaluation sommative en fin de session</p>
      </div>
      <div class="eval-item">
        <div class="eval-dot"></div>
        <p>Questionnaire de satisfaction à l'issue de la formation</p>
      </div>
      <div class="eval-item">
        <div class="eval-dot"></div>
        <p>Certificat de réalisation de l'action de formation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════ LOCALISATION ══════════════ -->
<section id="localisation">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Localisation</div>
    <h2>Où se déroule la formation ?</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;color:#555;font-size:0.95rem;">
      Cette formation peut se tenir <strong>dans vos locaux (intra)</strong> ou dans une salle mise à disposition (inter).<br>
      Elle est également disponible <strong>à distance</strong> via Teams, Zoom ou Google Meet.
    </p>
    <div style="background:var(--light);border-radius:14px;padding:2rem 2.5rem;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1.5rem;align-items:center;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:200px;">
        <p style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--marine);margin-bottom:0.4rem;">📍 Intra-entreprise</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#555;">La formation se déroule dans les locaux de votre entreprise. L'employeur met à disposition une salle équipée (vidéoprojecteur, paperboard, wifi).</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:200px;">
        <p style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--marine);margin-bottom:0.4rem;">🌐 À distance</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#555;">Chaque stagiaire doit disposer d'un ordinateur avec micro et accès internet. La caméra est obligatoire.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

